[{"id": 572524, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5218, "text": "Ey Peygamber! Kad\u0131nlar\u0131 bo\u015fayaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131zda, onlar\u0131 iddetlerini g\u00f6zeterek bo\u015fay\u0131n ve iddeti de say\u0131n. Rabbiniz Allah'tan korkun. Apa\u00e7\u0131k bir hayas\u0131zl\u0131k yapmalar\u0131 hali bir yana, onlar\u0131 evlerinden \u00e7\u0131karmay\u0131n, kendileri de \u00e7\u0131kmas\u0131nlar. Bunlar Allah'\u0131n s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131d\u0131r. Kim Allah'\u0131n s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131n\u0131 a\u015farsa, \u015f\u00fcphesiz kendine zulmetmi\u015f olur. Bilemezsin, olur ki Allah, bundan sonra bir durum ortaya \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131verir."}, {"id": 572525, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5219, "text": "\u0130ddet m\u00fcddetlerini doldurduklar\u0131nda onlar\u0131 ya me\u015fru \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fcler i\u00e7erisinde (nikah\u0131n\u0131z alt\u0131nda) tutun veya onlardan me\u015fru \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fclere g\u00f6re ayr\u0131l\u0131n. \u0130\u00e7inizden adalet sahibi iki ki\u015fiyi de \u015fahit tutun. \u015eahitli\u011fi Allah i\u00e7in yap\u0131n. \u0130\u015fte bu, Allah'a ve ahiret g\u00fcn\u00fcne inananlara verilen \u00f6\u011f\u00fctt\u00fcr. Kim Allah'tan korkarsa, Allah ona bir \u00e7\u0131k\u0131\u015f yolu ihsan eder."}, {"id": 572526, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5220, "text": "Ve ona beklemedi\u011fi yerden r\u0131z\u0131k verir. Kim Allah'a g\u00fcvenirse O, ona yeter. \u015e\u00fcphesiz Allah, emrini yerine getirendir. Allah her \u015fey i\u00e7in bir \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fc koymu\u015ftur."}, {"id": 572527, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5221, "text": "Kad\u0131nlar\u0131n\u0131z i\u00e7inden adetten kesilmi\u015f olanlarla, adet g\u00f6rmeyenler hususunda teredd\u00fct ederseniz, onlar\u0131n bekleme s\u00fcresi \u00fc\u00e7 ayd\u0131r. Gebe olanlar\u0131n bekleme s\u00fcresi ise, y\u00fcklerini b\u0131rakmalar\u0131 (do\u011fum yapmalar\u0131)d\u0131r. Kim Allah'tan korkarsa, Allah ona i\u015finde bir kolayl\u0131k verir."}, {"id": 572528, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5222, "text": "\u0130\u015fte bu, Allah'\u0131n size indirdi\u011fi buyru\u011fudur. Kim Allah'tan korkarsa Allah onun k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fcklerini \u00f6rter ve onun m\u00fckafat\u0131n\u0131 artt\u0131r\u0131r."}, {"id": 572529, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5223, "text": "Onlar\u0131 g\u00fcc\u00fcn\u00fcz \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fcs\u00fcnde oturdu\u011funuz yerin bir b\u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcnde oturtun, onlar\u0131 s\u0131k\u0131\u015ft\u0131r\u0131p (gitmelerini sa\u011flamak i\u00e7in) kendilerine zarar vermeye kalk\u0131\u015fmay\u0131n. E\u011fer hamile iseler, do\u011fum yap\u0131ncaya kadar nafakalar\u0131n\u0131 verin. Sizin i\u00e7in \u00e7ocu\u011fu emzirirlerse onlara \u00fccretlerini verin, aran\u0131zda uygun bir \u015fekilde anla\u015f\u0131n. E\u011fer anla\u015famazsan\u0131z \u00e7ocu\u011fu, ba\u015fka bir kad\u0131n emzirecektir."}, {"id": 572530, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5224, "text": "\u0130mkan\u0131 geni\u015f olan, nafakay\u0131 imkanlar\u0131na g\u00f6re versin; r\u0131zk\u0131 daralm\u0131\u015f bulunan da Allah'\u0131n kendisine verdi\u011fi kadar\u0131ndan nafaka \u00f6desin. Allah hi\u00e7 kimseyi verdi\u011fi imkandan fazlas\u0131yla y\u00fck\u00fcml\u00fc k\u0131lmaz. Allah, bir g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fckten sonra bir kolayl\u0131k yaratacakt\u0131r."}, {"id": 572531, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5225, "text": "Rabbinin ve O'nun el\u00e7ilerinin emrinden uzakla\u015f\u0131p azm\u0131\u015f nice memleketler vard\u0131r ki, biz onlar\u0131 (ahalisini) \u00e7etin bir hesaba \u00e7ekmi\u015f ve onlar\u0131 g\u00f6r\u00fclmemi\u015f azaba \u00e7arpt\u0131rm\u0131\u015f\u0131zd\u0131r."}, {"id": 572532, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5226, "text": "B\u00f6ylece onlar da yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 tatm\u0131\u015flar ve i\u015flerinin sonu tam bir h\u00fcsran olmu\u015ftur."}, {"id": 572533, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5227, "text": "Allah onlara \u015fiddetli bir azap haz\u0131rlam\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Ey inanan ak\u0131l sahipleri! Allah'tan korkun. Allah size ger\u00e7ekten bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 (kitap) indirmi\u015ftir."}, {"id": 572534, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5228, "text": "\u0130man edip salih amel i\u015fleyenleri, karanl\u0131klardan ayd\u0131nl\u0131\u011fa \u00e7\u0131karmak i\u00e7in size Allah'\u0131n apa\u00e7\u0131k ayetlerini okuyan bir Peygamber g\u00f6ndermi\u015ftir. Kim Allah'a inan\u0131r ve faydal\u0131 i\u015f yaparsa Allah onu, altlar\u0131ndan \u0131rmaklar akan, i\u00e7inde ebedi kalacaklar\u0131 cennetlere sokar. Allah o kimse i\u00e7in ger\u00e7ekten g\u00fczel bir r\u0131z\u0131k vermi\u015ftir."}, {"id": 572535, "identifier": "tr.vakfi", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Diyanet Vakf\u0131", "transelator_en_name": "Diyanet Vakfi", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5229, "text": "Allah, yedi kat g\u00f6\u011f\u00fc ve yerden bir o kadar\u0131n\u0131 yaratand\u0131r. Ferman bunlar aras\u0131ndan inip durmaktad\u0131r ki, b\u00f6ylece Allah'\u0131n her \u015feye kadir oldu\u011funu ve her \u015feyi ilmiyle ku\u015fatt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 bilesiniz."}]